    "description": "This collection contains the backend API endpoints for the **Notes App**. It covers the core operations needed to interact with the notes service running locally on port 3001:\n\n- **Add Note** (`POST /saveNotes`) – Creates and saves a new note to the backend.\n    \n- **Get Notes List** (`GET /getNotes`) – Retrieves the full list of saved notes.\n    \n\nUse this collection to develop, test, and validate the Notes App backend API during local development.",
